Images of the label for the RT-AC1750 show that it uses the MSQ-RTAC66U FCC ID. :Details for this device are copied from the [[ASUS RT-AC66U]]. As of 09/07/2017, the current latest firmware update provided for these two routers :(3.0.0.4.380.7743, dated 06/26/2017) is identical.
C:\>fc /b RT-AC1750_3.0.0.4_380_7743-g2cf84e9.trx RT-AC66U_3.0.0.4_380_7743-g2cf84e9.trx Comparing files RT-AC1750_3.0.0.4_380_7743-g2cf84e9.trx and RT-AC66U_3.0.0.4_380_7743-G2CF84E9.TRX FC: no differences encountered
